{"tid":2397230,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【回到未來・沈旭暉 】 假如制裁BNO5+1，那居英權藍絲家庭呢？","createTime":"2021-02-06T09:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-06T09:01:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ad869017d6d3bf759d1d0e4fd49d96b7fb349d98","tid":2397230,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T09:01:29.000Z","msg":"【回到未來・沈旭暉 036🇬🇧🇭🇰】<br />\n假如制裁BNO5+1，那居英權藍絲家庭呢？<br />\nFeb 4, 2021<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hslKLrfDk48\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhslKLrfDk48&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIQQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=7d699de1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hslKLrfDk48</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n堅離地球 &middot; 沈旭暉<br />\n192K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n中國政府強調要反制「BNO5+1移居計劃」，但根據同樣中國邏輯，林鄭月娥一家獲得英籍的「居英權計劃」，其實對國家安全有更大威脅。這個「港英deep state」論，在傳統左派當中非常盛行，他們對香港公務員的不信任，很大程度源於此。中國認為居英權計劃佈局周詳，把五萬個香港精英家庭綑綁到英籍，卻讓他們繼續在香港一邊工作，一邊效忠英女王，明顯是英方埋下的地雷。為了國家安全，北京應該怎樣看待獲得居英權的藍絲家庭？<br />\n<br />\n⏺ 全文見Patreon<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/posts/46915360​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fposts%2F46915360%E2%80%8B&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIQQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=e3219c99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.patreon.com/posts/46915360​</a><br />\n<br />\nSimon 沈旭暉 堅離地 Social Media ▶<br />\n⏺Patreon: <a href=\"http://www.patreon.com/simonshen​​​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fsimonshen%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIQQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=bcb71c6d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.patreon.com/simonshen​​​</a><br />\n🔼Facebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shensimon​​​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshensimon%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIQQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=6fd34ea6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shensimon​​​</a><br />\nℹ️Instag